OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with sunny spells for many.
OL,7,FBecoming increasingly cloudy, with
OL,8,Fshowers moving in from the northwest
OL,9,Fovernight. Showers may merge into
OL,10,Flonger spells of rain toward dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with early rain
OL,13,Ffollowed by sunny spells and blustery
OL,14,Fshowers on Tuesday, with a risk of
OL,15,Fhail and thunder. Feeling cool for the
OL,16,Ftime of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
