OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FSunshine and showers Wednesday with a
OL,7,Frisk of thunder. Rain arriving during
OL,8,FThursday. Friday, sunny spells perhaps
OL,9,Fwith rain or showers. Breezy at times.
OL,10,FRather cool, trending nearer normal.
